# glest: Estimation of the grouping loss of a probabilistic classifier

[![Binder](https://mybinder.org/badge_logo.svg)](https://mybinder.org/v2/gh/aperezlebel/glest.git/HEAD?labpath=examples%2Fexample.ipynb)
